                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 1 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি বৃত্ত x অক্ষকে (8, 0) বিন্দুতে স্পর্শ করে এবং y&nbsp;অক্ষ থেকে 12 দৈর্ঘ্যের জ্যা কেটে নেয়। বৃত্তের সমীকরণ =? &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="https://umsbd.net/Uploads/CkEditor_Images/1_68_51_276_9675_11072018_153546865_439985.jpg"><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 160px; height: 186px;"></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-5-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mn>6</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>8</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>64</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>64</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-75" style="width: 23.895em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 19.592em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1019.55em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-76"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-77" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">r</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-78" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>16</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#xB1;</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>64</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-106" style="width: 13.609em;                                         <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-9-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>39</mn><mo>&amp;gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-153" style="width: 17.666em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.469em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1014.43em, 2.338em, -999.998em); overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.453em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>39</mn><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-9">(-1)^2+5^2+4(-1)+3×5+2=39>0</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-10-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-181" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-182"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-183" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-10">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;বৃত্তের বাইরে&nbsp;</p>
</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বৃত্তটির কেন্দ্র&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-17-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-284" style="width: 6.355em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.207em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1005.17em, 2.338em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-295" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-296" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-17">(-3,\ 1),\ y=x</script></span>&nbsp;এর সাপেক্ষে এর প্রতিবিম্ব&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-19-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-307" style="width: 11.355em; top: -4.383em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-316" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-317" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-320" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-321" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">3</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-322"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.158em, 1000.29em, 4.387em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-323" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-324" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-325" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-326" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">16</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-19"> ∴(x-1)^2+(y+3)^2=16</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বৃত্তের কেন্দ্র&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-25-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>16</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-370" style="width: 14.223em; padding-left: 0.166em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-378" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-379" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-380" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">r</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-381" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-382" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.248em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1004.35em, 4.223em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-383"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-384" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">16</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-385" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; left: 2.092em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 2.625em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-389" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-390" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>∴</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>16</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-25">=(-4,2)∴r=\sqrt{16+4-4}=4</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-26-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>a</mi><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msup><mn>60</mn><mo>&amp;#x2218;</mo></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><msqrt><mn>3</mn></msqrt></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-391" style="width: 17.625em; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-565" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">10</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-566" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-567" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-568" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -3.948em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>40</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>14</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>56</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-31">(y-2)(y-8)+(x-10)(x-4)=0 \\ ⇒y^2-8y-2y+16+x^2-4x-10x+40=0 \\ ⇒x^2+y^2-14x-10y+56=0 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

</label>
                                                <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">

vertical-align: -0.747em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>4</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>4.2.</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-51">4-4.2.(1-a^2 )=0 ⇒ 4-8+8a^2 ⇒ a^2=\frac{1}{2}⇒ a=\frac{1}{\sqrt2}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>9 একক ব্যাসার্ধ বিশিষ্ট একটি বৃত্ত x ও y উভয় অক্ষকে স্পর্শ করে। বৃত্তটির সমীকরণ কোনটি?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>এখানে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-56-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x3B1;</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x3B2;</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-900" style="width: 2.707em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.215em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1002.13em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-901"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-902" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-903"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-904"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-905" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">α</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-906" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-907" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-908"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-909"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-910" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">β</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-911" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>α</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>β</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-56">(α,\ β)</script></span>&nbsp;বৃত্তের কেন্দ্র হলে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-57-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>|</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x3B1;</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>|</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x3B2;</mo></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-912" style="width: 7.379em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.027em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1005.99em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-913"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-914"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-915"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-916" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">|</span></span></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-917"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-918"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-919" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">α</span></span></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-920"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-921"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-922" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">|</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-923" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-58-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>e</mi><msup><mi>q</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>9</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-937" style="width: 14.428em; </span>

</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                </div>

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-73-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1168" style="width: 13.527em; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.132em, 1000.3em, 4.361em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1437" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.374em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1438" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1439" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1440" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">25</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.411em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>7</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-88">(x-7)^2+(y-5)^2=25</script></span>&nbsp;বৃত্তের একটি জ্যা কেন্দ্রে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-89-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mn>60</mn><mo>&amp;#x2218;</mo></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1441" style="width: 1.753em; top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1442"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1443"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.418em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বৃত্তের জ্যা কেন্দ্রে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-90-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mn>60</mn><mo>&amp;#x2218;</mo></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1446" style="width: 1.477em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1001.19em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1447"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1448"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1449" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">60</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1450" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">∘</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mn>60</mn><mo>∘</mo></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-90">60^\circ </script></span> কোণ উৎপন্ন করলে ঐ জ্যা এর দুই প্রান্ত ও কেন্দ্র মিলে সমবাহু ত্রিভুজ গঠন করে যার বাহুর দৈর্ঘ্য = ব্যাসার্ধ।</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-91-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mn>5</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1451" style="width: 1.477em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1001.15em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1452"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1453" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1454" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mn>5</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-91">∴5</script></span>&nbsp;একক।&nbsp;</p>

padding-left: 0.263em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1587" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.316em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.366em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-104">x^2+y^2-4x-8y=-4 </script></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;বৃত্তের একটি স্পর্শক নিচের কোনটি?&nbsp;</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

<p>কেন্দ্র হতে&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-111-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1652" style="width: 6.805em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 17 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>ত্রিভুজটি সমকোণী। এর পরিকেন্দ্র = অতিভুজের মধ্যবিন্দু। <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; padding-left: 0.289em;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1867" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1868" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1869" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1870" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2.</mn><mo>∴</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-128">x=\frac {3×8+2×3}{5}=6,\ \ y=2. ∴(6,2)</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>x অক্ষকে স্পর্শ করলে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-143-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2102" style="width: 2.748em; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-143">g^2=c</script></span>&nbsp;হয় বা,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2112" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2113" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2114" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2115" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">25</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2116" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2117" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2118" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2119" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>∴</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>±</mo><mn>5</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-144">a^2=25 ∴a=±5</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

<p>Here,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-151-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2208" style="width: 9.961em;                                 <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 23 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>পোলার স্থানাঙ্কে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-154-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2283" style="width: 3.467em;                                         <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 25 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি বৃত্তের দুইটি জ্যা বৃত্তের উপরিস্থিত একটি বিন্দুতে মিলিত হয়। জ্যাদ্বয়ের অপর প্রান্তদ্বয় বৃত্তের একটি ব্যাসের প্রান্তবিন্দু। জ্যাদ্বয়ের ঢাল&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 90px; height: 81px;"></p>

<p>বৃত্তের ব্যাস কর্তৃক উৎপন্ন কেন্দ্রস্থ কোণ এক&nbsp;সরলকোণ। জ্যা দুটির জন্য বৃত্তস্থ কোণ এক সমকোণ, ফলে তারা পরস্পর লম্ব।<br>
জ্যা দুটি এবং ব্যাস একটি সমকোণী ত্রিভুজ গঠন করে।</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-178-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2734" style="width: 6.232em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.084em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1005em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2735"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2736" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2737" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.314em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2738" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.863em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2739" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2740"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.314em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2741" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.863em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2742" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2743" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2744" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>সমকোণী ত্রিভুজে, পরিকেন্দ্র = অতিভুজের মধ্যবিন্দু&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>2.5</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-61" style="width: 4.223em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.445em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.314em, 1003.36em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-62"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-63" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-64" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-65" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-66" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-67" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-68" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2.5</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-69" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>2.5</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-7">∴(6,\ 2.5)</script></span>&nbsp;বিন্দু।&nbsp;</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কেন্দ্রে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-14-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mn>60</mn><mo>&amp;#x2218;</mo></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-143" style="width: 1.477em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1001.19em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-144"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-145"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-146" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">60</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-147" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">∘</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mn>60</mn><mo>∘</mo></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-14">60^\circ</script></span> তৈরি করলে এই জ্যা এর দুই প্রান্ত ও কেন্দ্র মিলে সমবাহু ত্রিভুজ গঠন করে যার বাহুর দৈর্ঘ্য = ব্যাসার্ধ। <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-15-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>p</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-148" style="width: 1.477em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1001.19em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-149"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-150" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-151" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">p</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.903em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi>p</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-15">\therefore p</script></span>&nbsp;একক।&nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 3 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-16-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-152" style="width: 6.112em; top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-153"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-154"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.008em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.561em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-156" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-157" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-158" style="padding-left: 0.225em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.971em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.43em, 1000.49em, 4.324em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-159" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.561em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-160" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-162" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-31-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mi>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>c</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>16</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-311" style="width: 18.732em; top: -4.096em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-341" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.747em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mi>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mi>c</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>16</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-31">r=\sqrt{g^2+f^2-c}=\sqrt{(-4)^2+3^2-16}=3</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-32-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x3C0;</mo></mrow><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-343" style="width: 11.027em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.018em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1009.02em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-344"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-345" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-346" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">A</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-347" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-348" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-349"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-350" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π</span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-351"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-353" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-354" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-355" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-356" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-357" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.45em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-358" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-359" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-360" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-361" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">9</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-362" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">π<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.252em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>π</mo></mrow><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn><mi>π</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-32">∴A=πr^2=\pi×3^2=9\pi</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>

                                            <p>একটি বৃত্ত x অক্ষকে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-33-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-363" style="width: 3.02em; padding-left: 0.289em;">25</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-463" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-464" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-465" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-466" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-467" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-468" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.068em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.53em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-469" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-470" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-471" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-472" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-473" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-474" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">25</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-475" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-476" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">16</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-477" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-478" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">c</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>4</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>;</mo><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>c</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-38">r=\sqrt{3^2+4^2}=5 ;r^2=25=g^2+f^2-c=25+16-c</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-39-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#xB1;</mo><mn>10</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-479" style="width: 17.174em; padding-left: 0.289em;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-483" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-484" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-489" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-490" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block;                                                 <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB1;</mo><mn>2</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-528" style="width: 1.551em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.277em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.414em, 1001.23em, 2.37em, -999.998em); top: -2.229em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-529"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-530" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">±</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-531" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>±</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-44">± 2</script></span></p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-45-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></mfrac><mo>.</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-532" style="width: 20.166em; <p>ভুজ 4 হলে কোটি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-46-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#xB1;</mo><msqrt><mn>4</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#xB1;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-575" style="width: 6.805em;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোন বৃত্তের সমান্তরাল 2 টি স্পর্শকের সমীকরণ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-48-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-605" style="width: 8.348em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.82em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1006.78em, 2.573em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.225em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-610" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">4</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-611" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-612" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-613" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>স্পর্শকদ্বয়ের দূরত্ব&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-54-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>R</mi><mo>.</mo><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&amp;#x2026;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-663" style="width: 13.158em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.781em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.314em, 1010.7em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-664"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-665" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-666" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-667" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">R</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-668" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">.</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-669" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.166em;">∴</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-670" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-671" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-672" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-673" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">4</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-674" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-675" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-676" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বৃত্তটির কেন্দ্র&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-63-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>.</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>x</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-839" style="width: 5.371em;                                         <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-65-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-877" style="width: 6.112em; width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-75">\left(-\frac{3}{2},\ -\frac{3}{2}\right)</script></span>&nbsp;বিন্দুগামী ও কেন্দ্রদ্বয়ের সংযোজক রেখার উপর লম্ব।&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-76-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1030" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1031"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1032" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-76">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;নির্ণেয় রেখা,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>প্রদত্ত বৃত্তের কেন্দ্র&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-83-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1090" style="width: 3.568em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.912em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1002.83em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1091"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1092" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1093" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1094" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1095" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1096" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 13 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি বৃত্তের দুইটি জ্যা বৃত্তের উপরিস্থিত একটি বিন্দুতে মিলিত হয়। জ্যাদ্বয়ের অপর প্রান্তদ্বয় বৃত্তের একটি ব্যাসের প্রান্তবিন্দু। জ্যাদ্বয়ের ঢাল&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-88-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1149" style="width: 1.604em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.306em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.678em, 1001.31em, 2.498em, -999.998em);
