                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 90px; height: 81px;"></p>

<p>বৃত্তের ব্যাস কর্তৃক উৎপন্ন কেন্দ্রস্থ কোণ এক&nbsp;সরলকোণ। জ্যা দুটির জন্য বৃত্তস্থ কোণ এক সমকোণ, ফলে তারা পরস্পর লম্ব।<br>
জ্যা দুটি এবং ব্যাস একটি সমকোণী ত্রিভুজ গঠন করে।</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-94-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1202" style="width: 6.232em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.084em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1005em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1203"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1204" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1205" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.314em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1206" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.863em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1207" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1208"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.314em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1209" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.863em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1210" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1211" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1212" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1213" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.247em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-94"> \therefore m_1m_2=-1</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বৃত্তটির কেন্দ্র&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-100-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2261;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>4</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1267" style="width: 4.059em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.322em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1003.24em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1268"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1269" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">≡</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1270" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">(</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1271" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1272" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1273" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1274" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1275" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>≡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>4</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-100">≡(-6,4)</script></span>&nbsp;যা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-101-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1276" style="width: 5.125em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.182em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1004.14em, 2.297em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1281" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1282" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1283" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1284" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-101">2x+3y=0</script></span>&nbsp;এর ওপর অবস্থিত।&nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 15 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                            <span>Question 16 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 17 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-122-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1641" style="width: 13.75em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কেন্দ্র&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-127-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>9</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1684" style="width: 14.51em; top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1685"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1686" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1687" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">(</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1688" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1689" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1690" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1691" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1692" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1693" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1694" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1695" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">r</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1696" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-1697" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.756em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; left: 3.199em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 0.453em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1705" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-141-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1899" style="width: 21.068em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-142-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1934" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1935"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1936" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-142">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;বৃত্তের ভিতরে&nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -3.948em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>15</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-149">(y-2)(y+1)+(x-5)(x+3)=0\\ ⇒y^2+y-2y-2+x^2+3x-5x-15=0 \\ ⇒x^2+y^2-2x-y-17=0 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-156-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>b</mi><mo>;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2167" style="width: 6.068em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.147em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>;</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-164">x+y=1 ⇒ y=1-x ; x^2+y^2=2ax\\ ⇒ x^2+1+x^2-2x=2ax⇒2x^2-2x(a+1)+1=0 </script></span></p>

<p>স্পর্শ&nbsp;করার পর্যাপ্ত শর্ত হলো,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-165-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x200D;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4.2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2330" style="width: 15.002em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 12.297em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1012.22em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2331"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2332" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2333"><span style="font-family: STIXGeneral, &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, serif; font-size: 82%; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;">&zwj;</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2334" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2335" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2336" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2337" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">1</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2338"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.158em, 1000.29em, 4.387em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2339" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2340" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2341" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2342" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">4.2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2343" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2344" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2345" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-2346" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2347" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2348" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2349" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2350" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-2351" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2352" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2353" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>4</mn><mo>&zwj;</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>4.2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-165">4 &zwj;(a+1)^2-4.2=0⇒ a^2+2a=1</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 180px; height: 46px;"></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-172-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>28</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>42</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>6</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2402" style="width: 15.002em; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2408" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">28</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2409" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">7</span><span style="display: inline-block; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-2416" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2417" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">42</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2418" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">7</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.82em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2419" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2420" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2421" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2422" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2423" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2424" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-2425" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-2426" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-2427" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>28</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>42</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>∴</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mn>6</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-172">\therefore x=\frac{28}{7}=4,\ y=\frac{42}{7}=6\therefore(4,\ 6)</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 24 </span>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 25 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>7 একক ব্যাসার্ধ বিশিষ্ট একটি বৃত্ত x ও y উভয় অক্ষকে স্পর্শ করে। বৃত্তটির সমীকরণ কোনটি?</p>

            <div class="row" style="margin-top:20px;">
                                <h4>Engineering Weekly Live Exam</h4>
                            </div>

















































<div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 1 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 90px; height: 86px;"></p>

<p>চিত্রে&nbsp;&nbsp;ABCD&nbsp;বর্গক্ষেত্রের প্রতি বাহুর দৈর্ঘ্য&nbsp;2&nbsp;একক হলে বৃত্তটির ক্ষেত্রফল কত বর্গ একক?</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-40" style="width: 0.658em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-8-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><msup><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-43" style="width: 5.248em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.305em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1004.3em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-44"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-45" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-46" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-50" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-51" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 2 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-9-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-53" style="width: 7.304em; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-57" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-58" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-59" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-60" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-61" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-62" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.134em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.048em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-9">x=3cos\theta+1 </script></span>&nbsp;এবং&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-10-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-64" style="width: 7.23em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.926em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1005.89em, 2.573em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-65"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-66" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-67" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-68" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-15-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2026;</mo><mo>.</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mspace linebreak=&quot;newline&quot; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.39em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.395em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-140" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">…</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-141" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-144" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-145" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-146" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-147" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.1em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>…</mo><mo>.</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>…</mo><mo>.</mo><mo>.</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-15">cos\theta=\frac{x-1}{3}\ldots.\ (i) \\ sin\theta=\frac{y-2}{3}\ldots..\ (ii) </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-16-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-148" style="width: 22.256em; vertical-align: -0.847em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.552em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-16">\therefore\left(\frac{x-1}{3}\right)^2+\left(\frac{y-2}{3}\right)^2=1\Rightarrow\left(x-1\right)^2+\left(y-2\right)^2=3^2 </script></span></p>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.797em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msqrt><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-32">=\ \sqrt{1+1-\frac{1}{2}+3\left(-\frac{1}{2}\right)+\frac{1}{2}}=\frac{1}{\sqrt2} </script></span>&nbsp;একক</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-41-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-479" style="width: 13.75em; <p>কেন্দ্র হতে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-48-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-547" style="width: 2.461em; </label>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-56-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-659" style="width: 10.248em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-57-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-675" style="width: 0.658em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-59-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>10</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-703" style="width: 13.117em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-708" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-709" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-710" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>পোলার স্থানাঙ্কে&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-60-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mfrac><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-723" style="width: 3.206em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.61em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1002.46em, 2.833em, -999.998em);                                             </div>
                                        </div>

position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-908" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">r</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-909" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-910" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-911" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">5</span><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-912"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-913"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-914" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.49em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.547em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-915" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">r</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-916" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-917" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-918"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-919" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-920" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-921" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-922" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-923" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-924" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-925" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-926" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-927" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-928" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-929" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-930" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">21</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-931" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-932" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.551em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.402em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>21</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mi>r</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>21</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-65">\left(x-\frac{5}{\sqrt2}\right)^2+\left(y-\frac{5}{\sqrt2}\right)^2=2^2\Rightarrow x^2+y^2-5\sqrt2\ \left(x+y\right)+21=0 \\

\therefore r^2-5\sqrt2r\left(cos\theta+sin\theta\right)+21=0 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 80px; height: 75px;"></p>

                                            <p>মূলবিন্দুগামী একটি বৃত্ত x&nbsp;ও&nbsp;y&nbsp;অক্ষের ধনাত্মক দিক হতে যথাক্রমে&nbsp;3 ও 4&nbsp;একক অংশ কর্তন করলে বৃত্তের সমীকরণ-</p>

overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1130" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1131" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">9</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1132" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1133" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msqrt><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>6.66</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-87">=\ \sqrt{\left(3+3\right)^2+\left(5+5\right)^2}-5=6.66 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 1.764em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1249" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 15 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>সমবাহু ত্রিভুজের শীর্ষ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-91-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1250" style="width: 3.951em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.243em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1003.13em, 2.61em, -999.998em); border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.392em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-96">
x^2+y^2+2x+2y+3=0 
</script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>সমবাহু ত্রিভুজের ভরকেন্দ্র ও পরিকেন্দ্র একই।</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-97-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1343" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1344"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1345" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-97">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;বৃত্তের সমীকরণ:&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-98-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1346" style="width: 18.199em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.92em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1014.92em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1347"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1348"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.486em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1354" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">1</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1355" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.506em; left: 3.035em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1356" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1357" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1358" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.552em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-98">\left(x-1\right)^2+\left(y-1\right)^2=\left(-1-1\right)^2+\left(2-1\right)^2</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-99-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1388" style="width: 12.133em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.92em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1009.88em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1389"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1390" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1391" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1392" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1393" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1394" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1395" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1396" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1397" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1402" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1403" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1404" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1405" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1406" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1407" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.412em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.559em, 1000.41em, 1.846em, -999.998em); height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0.253em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.152em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>–</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-112">– </script></span>&nbsp;বৃত্তের ব্যাসার্ধ, যেহেতু কেন্দ্রের ভুজ ঋণাত্মক।</p>

<p>&nbsp;স্পর্শবিন্দু&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-113-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2261;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo><mo>&amp;#x2261;</mo><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1496" style="width: 11.723em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.592em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1009.51em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1497"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1498" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">≡</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1499" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">(</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1500" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1501" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1502" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-119-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>|</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></mrow><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mfrac><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mrow><mo>|</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x00B1;</mo><mn>3</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1560" style="width: 17.83em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.592em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.805em, 1014.59em, 3.732em, -999.998em); top: -3.031em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1561"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1562"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1563" style="vertical-align: 1.109em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.289em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -3.277em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -2.58em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1564"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.49em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.547em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.035em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.747em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.152em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>|</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></mrow><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></mfrac><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mrow><mo>|</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>±</mo><mn>3</mn><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-119">\left|\frac{2\left(0\right)-0+c}{\sqrt5}\right|=3\Rightarrow\left|c\right|=3\sqrt5\ \ \therefore c=\pm3\sqrt5 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-100-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msqrt><msup><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1305" style="width: 11.109em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.1em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1009.06em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1306"><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-1307"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-103-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>24</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>13</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1369" style="width: 20.822em; </span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1614" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1615" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1616" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1617" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1618" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1619" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1016.36em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: 0.781em; left: 0em;"><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-1620" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1621" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1622" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1623" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1624" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1625" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">6</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1626" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1627" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1628" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1629" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1630" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1631" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1632" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1633" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1634" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1635" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1636" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">6</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1637" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1638" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1639" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1640" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1641" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 6.887em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -6.147em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 7.303em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>6</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>6</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-114">\rm g=\frac{-5}{2}\ ;\ \ f=\frac{6}{2}=3\ ,\ \ c=6 \\
x\left(2\right)+y\left(0\right)-\frac{5}{2}\left(x+2\right)+3\left(y+0\right)+6=0 \\
\Rightarrow2x-\frac{5}{2}x-5+3y+6=0 \\
\Rightarrow-x+6y+2=0\ \ \therefore x-6y-2=0 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-117-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><msqrt><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>11</mn></msqrt></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1667" style="width: 10.125em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.281em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.822em, 1008.28em, 2.379em, -999.998em);
