vertical-align: -0.398em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>2</mn><msqrt><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>11</mn></msqrt></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-117">\rm 2\sqrt{g^2-c}=2\sqrt{5^2+11}</script></span>&nbsp;একক = 12 একক ; কেন্দ্র&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-118-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1686" style="width: 3.035em;                                         <br>

top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1718"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1719" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1720" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1721" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1722" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1723" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1724" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1725" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1727" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1728" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1729" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1730" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1731" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1732" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1733" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1734" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1735" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1736" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1737" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1739" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1740" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1741" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1743" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1744" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1745" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1746" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">y</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1747" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1748" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1749" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-122">\rm2rcos\theta=r^2\Rightarrow2x=x^2+y^2\Rightarrow x^2+y^2-2x=0 </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-123-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1753" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1754"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1755" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-123">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;কেন্দ্র (1,0)</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1868" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">±</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1869" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">30</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1870" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1871" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">k</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1872" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1873" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">55</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1874" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1875" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1876" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.994em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.948em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.502em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>|</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi></mrow><msqrt><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>4</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></mfrac><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>±</mo><mn>30</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>55</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-130">\rm 6=\left|\frac{3\left(-3\right)+4\left(-4\right)+k}{\sqrt{3^2+4^2}}\right|\Rightarrow\ k-25=\pm30\Rightarrow k=55,-5</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                            <span>Question 30 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-141-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-2034" style="width: 13.713em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

(i) x-অক্ষকে স্পর্শ করে<br>
(ii) <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-27-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-327" style="width: 2.684em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.2em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1002.09em, 2.61em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-328"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-329" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-330" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-331" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-332" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.151em;">0</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-333" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.32em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-27">(0,0)</script></span> বিন্দুগামী<br>
(iii) বৃত্তের কেন্দ্র &nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-28-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-334" style="width: 3.653em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.982em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1002.87em, 2.61em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-335"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-336" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-337" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-338" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-339" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.151em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-340" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-341" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.32em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-28">(4,-3)</script></span><br>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কেন্দ্র&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-29-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>&amp;#x2260;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-342" style="width: 6.846em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.617em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.314em, 1005.58em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-343"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-344"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-345" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-346"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-347" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-348" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-349" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-350" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-351" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-352" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">,</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-353" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.166em;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-354" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≠</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-355" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-356" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>,</mo><mi>c</mi><mo>≠</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-29">\left(4,-3\right),c\neq0\therefore</script></span> মূলবিন্দুগামী নয়।<br>
<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-30-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>c</mi><mo>&amp;#x2260;</mo><msup><mi>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-357" style="width: 3.732em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.035em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1002.99em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-358"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-359" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-360" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≠</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-361" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-362" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-363" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-364" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.403em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>c</mi><mo>≠</mo><msup><mi>g</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-30">c\neq g^2\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;x- অক্ষকে স্পর্শ করে না।</p>

                                            <span>Question 6 </span>

                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-31-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>49</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-365" style="width: 6.746em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-49-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-515" style="width: 4.879em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.977em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1003.94em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-516"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-517"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-518" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-519" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-520" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-521" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-522" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-523" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-524" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-525" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-49">x^2+y^2-4</script></span> এ বিন্দুগুলো বসিয়ে পাই,<br>
<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-50-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>0</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>&amp;gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-526" style="width: 14.305em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>x- অক্ষকে ছেদ করলে, <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-61-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x00B1;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-675" style="width: 10.904em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.936em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1008.86em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-676"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-677" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-678" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-679" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-680" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-681" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-682" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-683" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-684" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-685" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-686" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-687" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-688" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-689" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">±</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-690" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>∴</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>±</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-61">y=0 \therefore x^2=1\therefore x=\pm1</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                                    <p><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong><br>
একটি বৃত্ত মূলবিন্দুগামী এবং Y- অক্ষকে স্পর্শ করে। বৃত্তটির কেন্দ্রের ভুজ 3।</p>

                                </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কেন্দ্র&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-66-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>0</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-750" style="width: 2.707em; <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-69-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-789" style="width: 8.281em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 10 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>বৃত্তটির যে ব্যাসের ঢাল 2, তার সমীকরণ হবে–</p>

                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-74-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-846" style="width: 14.797em;                                             <span>Question 12 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>পরিধিস্থ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-76-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-873" style="width: 4.771em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                            <span>Question 13 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>বৃত্তের কেন্দ্র (5, 2) এবং এটি (7, 3) বিন্দু দিয়ে যায়। বৃত্তের ব্যাসের দৈর্ঘ্য–&nbsp;</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

(ii) <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-92-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1060" style="width: 6.746em; <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-96-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msup><mi>f</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1138" style="width: 15.658em; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1141" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1142" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1146" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1147" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1148" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1149" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1150" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">;</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1151" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1152"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.068em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.53em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1153" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.617em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1154" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1155" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1156" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.502em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.158em, 1001.97em, 4.387em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1157"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1158" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1159"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1160" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1161" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1162" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.506em; left: 2.051em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1163" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1164" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1165" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1166" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1167" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">c</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.552em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msup><mi>f</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-96">f=-2,\ c=4\ ;\ f^2=\left(-2\right)^2=4=c&nbsp;</script></span><br>
<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-97-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1168" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1169"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1170" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-97">\therefore</script></span> y- অক্ষকে স্পর্শ করবে।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfrac><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-54" style="width: 20.207em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">

clip: rect(2.748em, 1001.03em, 4.797em, -999.998em); top: -4.137em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-309" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.552em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>8</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>8</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>53</mn><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-30">\left(8-3\right)^2+\left(8-2\right)^2-8>0\Rightarrow53>0</script></span>&nbsp;</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-42-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>100</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-624" style="width: 7.342em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 160px; height: 110px;"><br>
কেন্দ্র (0,0) । জ্যা এর ওপর লম্বের ঢাল <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-48-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-688" style="width: 2.379em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-62-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>y</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-835" style="width: 11.355em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 13 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>উভয় সরলরেখার উপর লম্ব এবং বৃত্তটির কেন্দ্রগামী সরলরেখাটির সমীকরণ-</p>

width: 0px; height: 2.051em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>7</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-92">\left(\frac{7}{2},\frac{1}{2}\right)</script></span> বিন্দুগামী বলে, <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-93-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>13</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1400" style="width: 3.527em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>y- অক্ষকে ছেদ করলে, <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-99-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1460" style="width: 2.461em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.01em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1001.97em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1461"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1462" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1463" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1464" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.953em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-99">x=0 </script></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-100-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x00B1;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1465" style="width: 8.404em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.887em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1006.8em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1466"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1467" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1468" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1469" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1470" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1471" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1472" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1473" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1474" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1475" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1476" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1477" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">±</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1478" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msup><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>±</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-100">\therefore y^2=1\ \therefore y=\pm1&nbsp;</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 15 </span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-101-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>8</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1479" style="width: 3.653em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.982em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1002.87em, 2.61em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1480"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1481" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1482" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1483" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1484" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.151em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1485" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1486" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.32em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-101">(4,-8) </script></span>&nbsp;কেন্দ্রবিশিষ্ট বৃত্তটি y-অক্ষকে স্পর্শ করে, বৃত্তের ব্যাসার্ধ কত?</p>
